#icon: SOP/triangulate2d
#context: sop
#type: node

= Triangle Grid qL =

*Version 0.0.1*

"""Generates a grid of well placed triangles."""

@Parameters
    Orientation:
        Orientation of the generated grid.
    Size:
        Size of the generated grid.
    Center:
        Center of the generated grid.
    Rows:
        Number of rows.
    Columns:
        Number of columns.

@Limitations
    Nor symetric, nor straight edges are implemented.

@Release_Notes
    Version 0.0.1:
        Pre-release. Both simetric and straight edges should be implemented for a normal release.